      "text": [
        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"بَرُّوا آبَاءَكُمْ يَبَرَّكُمْ أَبْنَاؤُكُمْ وَ عِفُّوا عَنْ نِسَاءِ اَلنَّاسِ تَعِفَّ نِسَاؤُكُمْ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4985 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"Be good to your parents, and your children will be good to you. Remain chaste concerning the women of others, and your women will remain chaste.\""
        ]
      }
    },
